game.name: Lets go Fishing
game.description:
Fishing in a pond is a great fun in itself! Do you also love fishing? Are you searching for an online platform where you can practice your favorite sports activity in a friendly environment? Luckily, you have reached at the right place since we have today got you covered with a brand new sports game where you have to catch fishes with different designs and market value. Be careful friends as you have a limited time period to complete your task in Lets go Fishing!

Click or tap the screen to launch the hook and reach the goal to clear each level! The deeper you go, the more fishes you can bring with you at your home. Try to catch the higher-value fishes since they will help you to reach your goal faster! Your every successful fish catching will help you earn some money. Use the money you earn through your great work to unlock high-value fishes in this HTML5 fishing game!

Try to complete your level goal before the time runs out! You cannot move to the advanced level until you achieve the objective of the present level. Track your level, target score and time by looking at the bottom part of the screen! You can track your present score by looking at the top middle part of the screen. Hurry up, friends! Time is running very fast. Good luck to achieve you to earn maximum money by catching higher-value fishes in each level! Have fun for free without the tension of downloading games online!
